wikipedia_page.main: Frankie Jay Sutherland (born 6 December 1993) is a professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Southern League side, Farnborough. A QPR academy graduate, Sutherland has also spent time on loan at Portsmouth, and has represented the Republic of Ireland at youth level.
